name: Highway Heretics
description: In the radioactive ashes of the old world, wasteland warriors, vicious Vandals, and scrappy survivors war with one another for control over all that's left.

skinlines.name: Road Warrior
skinlines.description: Out in the wasteland, the only gospel a Road Warrior needs is the hum of an engine, and the only prayers they hear are the curses of their enemies.

skinlines.name: Vandal
skinlines.description: The Vandals loom large over the wasteland. They are a gang of violent thugs prone to mass destruction, brutal beatdowns, and wanton murderâ€¦ but they sure have a good time doing it.
